    "FR-SOS-018","simpleos-os_scheduler","simpleos-os_scheduler","simpleos-os scheduler","Add idle-path balancing and full wakeup preemption","Extend the conservative unblock/timer rebalance hooks with idle-pull balancing and fair-class wakeup preemption. Woken interactive/fair tasks should be able to preempt when their eligible virtual deadline is earlier than the current running","current","P1","doc/08_tracking/feature/simpleos_os_requests.md","","","","","`doc/05_design/scheduler_process_isolation.md`","","","","","","","","","","","2026-04-20","2026-04-20",true
    "FR-SOS-019","simpleos-os_scheduler","simpleos-os_scheduler","simpleos-os scheduler","Add RT bandwidth throttling and priority inheritance","Add safety controls before exposing unrestricted realtime policy to user workloads: global/per-CPU RT bandwidth throttling and priority-inheritance mutex support for bounded priority inversion.","current","P1","doc/08_tracking/feature/simpleos_os_requests.md","","","","","`doc/05_design/scheduler_process_isolation.md`","","","","","","","","","","","2026-04-20","2026-04-20",true
